text_info.text_contents:
I look forward to working
with you in the future.

Oh, I was flying and got caught
in a net. Did you save me?

Let's work together to
achieve our goals!

Am I supposed to greet you?
Well... nice to meet you!
We've met for the first time, right?

I never thought I would talk
to a human being.

If it's okay with you, I'd like
to help out.

Woah!
What will happen with me now!?

Uh, are you in trouble?
Can I help you?

I guess I got caught.
Nice job.

Wow, a human! I never thought
I would meet one!

This is the first time I've
spoken to a human.
What should I do from now on?

Oh, uhm, hello.
I hope we can get along.

Are you sure you want me?
Did you make a mistake?
What do you need me for?

Woah, a human!?
It's nice to meet you!

Huh? What is this place?
I was just flying around...

What?
What does a human need me for?

Well, if you're fine with me,
it's an honor to meet you.
You and I are gonna be busy.

I'll take care of you from now on.
Nice to meet you.
Is this some kind of request?

You've been looking at me for a bit.
Is something wrong?

Do you want to be friends?
Well, I'll do my best!
I feel a strong kinship with you.

Hello.
Were you also flying around?

Nice to meet you.
Where are we going?

Nice to meet you!
Let's be good friends.

Hello! I'm a Denpa Man, and
we live in... oh, you knew?

That was scary.
Please don't eat me, okay?

Oh, do you need help?
What can I do for you?

Wow, you're okay with me?
Really? Nice to meet you.

Wow, you're a human, aren't you?
Nice to meet you.

You surprised me!
I'm still a little dazed.

Gah, I was out of it.
I don't fly much these days.

You can see me?
That's amazing!

You're bringing me along?
Do we have enough supplies?
I hope you got a good look at me.

Your aim is really accurate!
Bravo!

Did I just get caught?
...It can't be helped, then.
Wow, what am I gonna do now?!

Does it look like we're flying?
Or is it more like swimming?

I hope you look forward to seeing
my skills.
I hope you use me wisely.

Our success depends on trust.
Will you trust me?

I hope I can meet your demands.
Let's do our best!

I'm a little busy right now,
are you in a hurry?

I'll behave! I promise!
Please don't do that again.

I hope we can be good friends.
Let's push each other ahead!

I don't know why I'm here.
Do you have any ideas?

What is it?
I'm not scared of you at all!

Is something wrong?
I'll lend you a hand.

What the...? Don't do anything bad!
I'll sue you!
What can I do for you?

You're human, aren't you?
I'm a Denpa Man!
Please don't scare me like that.

It may be a little sudden,
but I'm glad you found me.

Let's set the record straight.
Who are you?

Let's be honest with each other,
okay?

I thought I could avoid it.
You're pretty good.

You caught me!
What was the reason?
We're strangers, but... let's be friends.
I thought you couldn't see me.
I'm quite a sight, aren't I?

What are you going to do
with me from now on?

What will you do with me?
I will follow your decision.

Do you want to go with me?
I'm honored!

Something strange just attacked me.
Could you hide me for a second?

I lost, didn't I?
I want a rematch! C'mon!
You chose me over all the others!?

Can you see us? 
How strange.
Do you need me for something?

I usually fly gracefully.
I was a bit careless.

That was a nice catch.
Alright, I'll join you, then.

Somehow, I feel like I've been
waiting for you all this time!

This is our first meeting, right?
Nice to meet you!

Is everything alright?
Do you need someone to talk to?

You're a human, aren't you? Are you
seeing things you shouldn't?

Are you a human being?
That's amazing. You're enormous.

That was a good catch!
Let me tag along with you!

Wow, that was fun!
Let's try again!

Did you predict my movements?
I thought I was safe!

Well, I've got some free time.
I'll go with you.

When we travel together, nothing
will scare us anymore.

Well, I was bored...
Do you have something fun for me?

Let's see the whole
world together!

Are we going to team up?
You have some fierce eyes.

You can see me?
That's awesome! You're awesome!

Go and take me with you!
You won't regret it, right?

Oh no, this is the end.
Don't cook me!

Are we doing a staring contest?
Or are we trying not to laugh?

Let's stick together from now on.
Onward!

I was caught? Oh, well...
You're in charge now.

You look a bit surprised.
Do you want me to join you?

If you really needed my help,
you should have just told me.

Oh, please don't be scared.
My strength will help you.

Huh? I'm practicing my flight!
Don't mess me up!

You can see us? That's strange.
Are you a giant Denpa Man?

Hah... that was a good workout.
Can I take a break for now?

So you've made up your mind...
Huh. I like you!

It's nice to meet you!
Let's travel together!
Hey, will you play with me?
Let's be together from now on.
I love fun things! Let's go!

It's my first time meeting
a human friend!

We need your help! Nets are attacking us!
They attacked me, too!

We can play together.
What do you wanna do?
I thought I was able to avoid it.

Woah!
Your face is so big and scary!
Will I get paid if I help you out?

You're amazing.
I couldn't get away from you!

Are we friends from now on?
Hehe, nice to meet you.

Where are we going now?
I'm excited.

Are you a demon?
Should I catch you instead?

Hello. Nice to meet you!
A proper greeting is important.

I can't go along with strangers.
Please introduce yourself, okay?

Wow, that was awesome!
Let's keep playing together!

Will you take good care of me?
If you won't, please let me go.

Will you take me with you?
I'll do my best!
Are you going to take me to a fun place?

Aw, it was getting interesting.
Do you wanna try again?

Nice to meet you!
You should say it too, it's polite.

I was caught off guard!
That wasn't fair!

I'm strong.
And I look good too. Bonus.

I'm good at flying, aren't I?
What do you think?

Do you need my help?
That's fine. I'll be good.

Do you want to take me with you?
That's fine! Sounds interesting!

Fighting is so barbaric...
You're gonna make me do it?

I can't believe you're so gentle,
even though you're a giant.
Oh, do you want me to do something?
You can stay with me, I suppose.

Alas, a fated encounter!
Are you a chosen one?
Wow! Take a look at this!

I'm bad at conversations.
I'll... join you if you like.

Ugh, just shut up and take me.
I'm not in a good mood.

What should I do?
I think... I'll follow you.

Let's get along well.
I've never met someone like you.

It would have been nice if you
enjoyed the chase a little more.
Oh, hi. Um, it's my pleasure.

I hope you're not a boring person.
Will you make this fun for us?

I may have been waiting
for someone like you!

Do you need me?
I can follow you for now.

Do you want to take me along?
I guess it can't be helped.
My beauty is a sin, isn't it?
Can you take care of me?

As long as you get me stuff,
I'll gladly go with you.

I can't believe you caught me.
You're lucky today, aren't you?

You mean you're scouting me?
Yeah, I'm cute after all! Right!?

I can go with you, but has
anyone told you that you're cute?
Hmm. If it's you, then it's fine.

If you catch someone, own up to it.
You WILL take me, right?

Is this a fateful meeting?
Wow...

Give me strong enemies!
I don't want to slack off.

I was just getting tired of flying.
I'll rest at your place.

If you're taking me, then
I hope you give me things to do.

Oh, you're taking me?
Let's have fun.

I want to see the world,
 so take me with you, okay?

Okay, human.
What are you going to do with me?

It's not a bad idea to make friends.
We'll look after each other.

I know I'm cute, but you
shouldn't chase me like that!
You should be a little more gentle.

I'll say it, I'm neither
a dragonfly, or a fish

Thank you for inviting me.
It was quite aggressive, though.

I wonder if this is the
first time we've met?

Who are you?
What do you want?
Today is the beginning of our legend.
I can't say that I don't want to rely on you.

Oh my goodness, I didn't know
I was going to be caught.

A gentleman must greet everybody.
Are you polite enough?
I'm glad to have met you.
Did it look like I needed you?

If you chose me, it means
you need my help, right?

Oh, that scared me.
You woke me up!

Woo-hoo! 
I'll take care of you from now on!
Oh, you, can you see me?

I don't know what you need.
But no challenge is too much for me!

I saw your power from far away.
You should see mine, too!

If you need some friends to help you,
you should just ask, you know.
What kind of recruitment is this?

This must be some kind of destiny.
Let's cherish this moment.

What a wild invitation.
Who do you think I am?

That was a little
rough, don't you think?

Ha ha ha!
I am quite amazing, aren't I?

I was taking a walk.
What is this place?

It can't be helped.
I'll hear you out.

Hello, nice to meet you.
Are you having a good day?

From now on, I'll be your leader!
Huh? You're the leader instead?

Don't get too excited.
I'll go with you for now.

You're lucky to meet me!
You think so too, right?

I can't believe you chose me.
You look a little demanding.

Wait, if you can see me...
Are you a special kind of human?

Why did it have to be me...?
Fine, I'll go with you.

I'll give you the right
to take care of me.

You decided on me?
Well, I'll do my best for you.

If you're gonna take me,
treat me well, okay?

You want to be friends with me?
Well, you seem to have honest eyes.

You're taking me with you?
Well, make it fun, at least.

You're brave to look down on me.
I'll blow your mind!
I get the feeling I'm in trouble...
Thanks for taking me with you.
Oh, hello. How are you doing?
Well, well. I'll go with you.
Is there anything I can do for you?

Oh, it's a human.
Wait... you can see me?

Boil me, bake me...
Do whatever you want!

Did I disappoint you?
I'm sorry about that.

Hey, are you a human?
How come you can see me?

Oh, you needed me?
I'm sorry I was a hassle to catch.
You have a very unusual face.

I'm too lazy to complain.
Just take me.

This is kind of inconvenient...
Well, I'll come along, then.

A Denpa Man was just kidnapped!
You're the real culprit!

This is my first time talking to a human.
What language do you speak?

Please take me with you.
You have life insurance, right?
Heh heh, you're going to be surprised.

I feel like a bug caught by a spider.
What will you do with me?

What's wrong with your eyes?
They look fierce.
I hate complicated things. What about you?

How troublesome.
I'll leave it all up to you.

I-It's not that I couldn't dodge!
It was totally on purpose!

Please don't eat me.
I don't taste good.

I'm in real trouble now...
Where will you take me?
I'm a bit cynical, you know.

Did you see me looking at you?
You're quite observant.

Whether I can be useful or not
depends on how you raise me!

Have you been charmed by my loveliness?
I don't understand human tastes.

Do you see any marks of the net
on my face?

Did you catch me because you
couldn't decide? Not a good strategy...

What are you going to do with me?
You can't cook me even if you try!

What can I do for you?
I hope I can be of service.

If I don't train, I can't
use my antenna... Can you help me?
Can you help me develop my talents?

Even if I can't do much right now...
will you believe in me and my skill?

I need some help developing my skills.
Can you do that for me?

The antenna that grows on my head...
Please don't waste it.

If you raise me well, I'm sure
I can do something amazing.

I have a very promising future.
I'll be very strong!

Do you mind if I'm not immediately
strong? I'm motivated enough to train!

It seems that I have a hidden power!
You have to help me unleash it!

Hey, you!
Do you think I'll have an awesome skill?

Can you help me grow my antenna?
It's not that cool right now...

I want to have my skill ASAP.
I'm counting on you!

If you take me along, I might
be able to help you one day!

I'm sure I'll be great someday.
You think so too, right? Right?

I don't know what I can do to help.
I look forward to when I can!

I can do amazing things.
Well, not yet, but someday I will!

The antenna on my head is growing.
I wonder what it will be?

My antenna is still in preparation.
I hope I can use it soon...

My potential slumbers in the root.
But one day, it'll be ready!

Were you looking for my special skill?
Is it okay if I can't use it yet?

If you help me get stronger,
I can help you in return!

I still can't use my antenna.
Can you help me fix that, please?

What will my skill turn out like?
Take me with you and find out!

What do you think of someone with secrets?
Mysterious and intriguing, right?

I hope that you can draw on
my strength to help you. Can you?
Do you think I can be considered talented?

Do not think of me as being
just like other Denpa Men, okay?
One day, you'll know all my secrets.

My hidden potential...
I need your help to find it.

Do I have a root on top of my head?
It's not for decoration, right?

Is my skill one of a kind?
...I wish I knew.
I can't share my secret with you yet!

Oh, are you taking me along?
Don't be too worried about my head.
I haven't been serious about training...
I'll take good care of everyone's HP!

If you can recover your health,
adventures may become a lot less scary.

If any of our friends get hurt,
I can take care of them.

Please let me take care
of your injuries.

Are the monsters too strong?
I can help out.

Adventuring can get dangerous.
I'll treat the wounded with my power!

Leave the healing up to me. You can
fight instead. Good strategy, right?

If I'm here, you won't need medicine.
You do want a healer, right?

Are you wounded?
I can fix it, can't I?

I may not look it, but
I'm good at healing. Were you surprised?

Injuries can be a symbol of pride,
but you don't always need them.

I'm good at healing wounds.
I do often get injured...

Even if everyone is injured,
I can help out!

Please take me along! C'mon!
My skill is really good!

It's okay if you don't like medicine!
I'll help you recover.
If you get hurt, I'll fix it for you.

If you get beat up too badly,
I'll take care of you.

I'm very good at healing.
Do you need my help, too?

I'll get you in shape.
It won't hurt at all, so sit still.

You must be feeling a little tired.
Do you need healing?

Well, you can leave it to me
to take care of the wounded.

As a leader, you have to
look after your whole team.

I don't like the over-reliance on medicines.
I prefer using my skill, instead.

You need more than offense to win.
Hopefully, I can help you with that.

I'm good at taking care of others.
Fighting on the other hand...

Were you hurt somewhere？
I can fix it for you.

My antenna happens to be popular
with kids. Do you like it?

There's no wound I can't heal!
...If they're not downed, that is.

Just attacking isn't good enough to win.
Use my skill as much as you like.

It's tough to fight with downed allies.
I can help them get back up!

I can help revive allies
if they've been downed!

When push comes to shove,
I might be able to help out!

It's a good idea to conserve
my skill for when you really need it.

Even if my friends are downed,
as long as I'm safe, it'll work out.

Please don't fight recklessly,
my skill can only go so far.

If you don't manage to heal in time,
I'll be your last resort.

We should work together when fighting.
Cooperation is very important.
I'll take care of the fallen ones!

I can revitalize anybody!
Just one try will leave you wide awake!

I want to fight with those
who never give up, no matter what.
I'll help anyone who gets knocked down.

Do you strugtle to heal on time?
Then leave it to me!

Do you get sad when a friend goes down?
In my case, I can help them out.

There's nothing to fear when we fight!
My skill will help those who can't get up!

Do you think I look like an angel?
I can revive my allies, after all.

I can help anybody who's been downed.
Fighting alone is scary, after all.

Not giving up until the very end
is a very admirable trait.

Would you like a wake-up kiss?
You won't sleep for as long as I'm around.

As long as I'm with you,
I won't allow our allies to go down!
Am I not the ultimate trump card?

I'm very good at making a turnabout!
You might be able to win with me!

As long as I'm able to fight,
we'll have a chance of winning!

I can fight until the very end.
I won't slow you down.

It's hard to fight when friends go down.
I'll make sure that doesn't happen.

Is it good to be so stubborn?
In the end, we've all gone down at least once.

If I'm healthy, I can help you out!
Please make my defenses good.

If there's anybody weak to flames,
I can help settle the score!

I can manipulate fire as much as I want.
Be careful around me, okay?
Please be careful with the sparks of fire.

It's easy to burn things when
I'm around. Don't be reckless!

Plants and ice monsters have
nothing on me at all!

When you deal with fire,
you get used to it.

If there's monsters weak to fire,
then I think I can help you.

It can be hard to get used to the heat.
I'm very good at burning things, though.

If anybody gets in your way,
I can just burn them!
There's nothing I can't burn with my flames!

My flames will burn the sky!
My flames will burn it all!

Oh, this fire isn't for show.
I've got powerful flames!

I'm able to sway fire as I please.
It's fun to watch.

My flames are scorching hot!
I'll be fine, but you should be careful.

Oh, you're taking me?
If you're not careful, you'll get burned.

I'll warm you up with
my flaming hot skill!

I'll help you out with
any plant based baddies, okay?
Can you feel my scorching fire?

My flames are very beautiful.
Do you want to see?

It's dangerous to play with fire.
Make sure to be careful.

I hope you let me show
off the power of fire!

Would you say your heart burns like fire?
Red, hot, and passionate?
Can I turn up the heat?

Do you need some company?
Sorry in advance if I burn you.

If you're not careful, you
might find some charred junk...
Do you like your steak well-done?

If there's any fire enemies,
I can take care of them.

My antenna lets me use water at will!
Now tell me, can you swim?

My skill will sweep foes off their feet!
Nobody stands a chance against my waves.

Please don't try to swim in my water.
You'll be swept away if you try...

If you need anybody to put out fires,
I'm right here.

Even water can be used offensively
with enough pressure.

I'll ask you just in case.
Can you swim?

You need some water, right?
You can never have too much water!

There's no way you can't
get on this stream, right?

The important thing is high pressure.
Even water can be powerful.

I'll push the enemy away with water!
So don't drown, okay?

If the enemy is tough,
some water can help you out!

Hey, you.
Are you good at swimming?

Do you want to take a bath? I can fill
it for you as much as you need!

If there's a fire somewhere,
I'll put it out right away.

If you need a bath, just tell me.
But I can't promise it won't overflow.

I'm quite a refined person,
even if my skill washes away my foes.

Do you want to surf on my waves?
I'm sure you'll love it!

I don't care if monsters
are drowned by my charm.
No flames are a match for my water!

Hey, would you like to swim with me?
I don't mind getting soaked.

If you need swimming lessons,
I may be able to help.

Even water droplets can tear through rock.
I'll show you how scary water is.

Do you know how to swim or not?
Do you need special training?

You won't be short of water with me.
Do you think that's a problem?

Let all your worries wash away.
In battle and in life.

Do you need my skill for something?
I'm sure you do!

Lightning is beautiful, isn't it?
I hope you don't hate it.

Water creatures tremble at my skill!
Please give it a try!

My skill might be more decisive
in a damp place.

Lightning and thunder are at my whim.
It's a very natural skill, right?

I can manipulate lightning.
Could you say I'm a generator?

My electricity isn't for home use.
Please use it appropriately.

My skill will shock you to your
very core!

Don't touch me with wet hands, okay?
You might get an electric shock.

If your doorknob ever zaps you,
that might be my fault. Sorry.

I'll numb any and all water foes
with my electrifying power!

What I use is electricity.
I'm water's worst nightmare.

Do you want to see my skill?
It'll crackle and pop!

I can't power a room, but
in battle, my electricity rocks!

My domain is electricity. It may be
dangerous if you touch me in rain.

If anyone gets in my way,
am I allowed to zap them?

Are you nervous? I'm not
in a bad mood, don't worry.

Are you scared?
You might falling for me!

If you touch me, you might
get an electric shock.

Saving electricity is important,
but don't worry about me.

My whole body is numb.
Can you withstand this shock?

Hey, you. What does it mean
to be a god of thunder?

I just like my brave composition.
That's shocking enough, right?

It's important to take care of
electricity! I also cherish it!

My skill is good for zapping!
I can't charge your 3DS, though.

Are you saving electricity?
I'm like a battery, you know?

I might have overcharged myself...
Ow ow ow...

I wield the power of the earth.
Those thunder folks better look out.

My skill lets me manipulate
the ground. Watch your footing.

Don't fall down and get muddy.
Please be careful.

I don't hate playing with soil.
Beautiful flowers need good soil.

You should keep calm,
and maintain steady footing.

As long as your feet are on the ground,
you can't escape from the earth.

I can fight with mud, but I don't like it.
I'm not used to being dirty.

If I move, so will the earth
beneath me!

Playing with mud makes me feel young.
But it's a lot of fun, isn't it?

It's useless to try and run away.
You can't escape my earth power!

My skill lets me control the earth!
But it won't let me fertilize crops.

I can use the earth to fight.
It protects me from harm, too.

Do you want to play in the mud?
No? Aww...

Let's play a lot!
Don't worry about mud stains!

The ground we walk on is heavy.
My skill will crush our foes!
The ground is warm, isn't it?

Isn't Mother Nature the earth itself?
...Am I using her gifts to fight?

My skill is all about mud.
Don't worry, we won't get dirty.

The mud feels nice today.
Would you like a mud bath?

Do you wanna see me
throw around chunks of mud?

The monsters will feel the wrath
of the earth itself!

The quality of soil depends on
location. Do you wanna see?

If you're scared of a big enemy,
I can help you crawl into a hole.

I'm very good at burying things.
Especially any electric monsters.

Mind your footing when you
happen to be around me.

My skill is quite good with mud.
Nobody could possibly escape me.

You think I'm dirty, huh?
If you do, I'll make YOU dirty for real!

Soil has a sense of stability, right?
Do you think I'm stable?

When you feel the gentle breeze,
it cleanses your heart, right?

Wind can come from many different
places, depending on where you are.

I can use the wind to give enemies
a cold! It may be a little intense...

From a gentle breeze to a
harsh storm, I can do it all!

I can blow your mind with my wind power!
Any earth foe will turn into dirt!
No enemy will escape my whirlwinds!
Let my wind power bring us victory.

Will you stand tall against the wind?
Don't worry, my power is on your side.

Blow away all the bad things.
All the monsters, everything.

I'll blow away anyone
who stands in my way!

Push through like a strong breeze!
Don't let anyone hold you back!

I'll help you push on with my power!
Don't get knocked down, now!

My power can be likened to a hurricane.
Don't look away, now.

I can move the wind whenever I want.
Whooosh.

Do you want to fly, too?
Can I use my skill to help?

My skill is all about wind power!
I'll blow away whatever bothers you.

Did you need a Denpa Man to
cool you down? My wind is gentle...

Faster, faster!
My wind power is strong AND fast!

Watch out. I don't wanna give
you a cold or anything.

If you get in my way,
you'll be sent flying! So don't.

The breeze makes me feel like
I'm free of any trouble.

Let's walk together as the wind
graces us. Blow all those monsters away.

The winds of change are coming.
But I can't wait. I want to feel it.

You look heavy. Are you immune to wind?
...Surely that's not true.

I will guide the wind
that sends you flying.

I want the wind to take me
with it as I fly away.

You could say I'm a walking
air conditioner, or a tiny fan.

Have you done your laundry well? If your
clothes fly off, it's not my fault.
Would you like to cool down?

I don't want to be cold to others.
But I do want to use my skill!

Ice is a little similar to glass.
But it's harder, sharper, and prettier.

My skill will cool everything down!
Do you have a jacket, just in case?

Do I look cold-hearted?
I'm more cool-headed, if you ask me.

If you're not good with the cold,
you can leave it to me.

I'm not good at being hotheaded.
Being cool is more my thing.

My skill attacks monsters with ice shards.
